gov.anl.ipns.ViewTools.Layouts
Class ViewerEnum

java.lang.Object
  gov.anl.ipns.ViewTools.Layouts.ViewerEnum

public class ViewerEnum
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a single location for the list of all ViewComponents, ComponentSwappers, and LayoutManagers. This class will help fill the void of enumerated types in Java 1.4 for the viewer structure. Any time a new view component, swapper, or layout manager is created, it should be added to this list.
